{"tid":2068034,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"天海祐希獲選為最光芒四射的中女","createTime":"2020-06-17T11:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T12:30:44.000Z","uid":16659,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f1f55b12016c9090096be99ff1937304e84a8db0","tid":2068034,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:21:58.000Z","msg":"日本《Mainichi Kirei》網站通過40多歲至50多歲女士，投票選出「你認為最光芒四射的40代50代女藝人」，結果52歲女星天海祐希以17.8%票數奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n網友大讚天海祐希表面爽朗，內裏則十分細心，像華麗的女王，值得信賴的上司，無論內到外都很美，甚至比男士更型。至於2至5位分別是50歲的石田百合子、44歲米倉涼子、46歲篠原涼子和43歲的井川遙。網友大讚石田百合子甚麽時候都給人年輕可愛感覺，有一份少女的透明感，又讚她外表好看，內裏有豐富內涵。而米倉涼子則給人非常自信，勇於挑戰任何事感覺，是出色的女子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200617/bkn-20200617170424736-0617_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200617%2Fbkn-20200617170424736-0617_00862_001.html&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wW5ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=d3d95fff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200617/bkn-20200617170424736-0617_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"df76755990f2e13b7ac840febe043d8f64dd8b5c","tid":2068034,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200617/photo/bkn-20200617170424736-0617_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200617170500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200617%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200617170424736-0617_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200617170500&h=4f2ca12e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天海祐希獲讚內到外都很美，比男士更型。"},{"pid":"4d6c51fc719c4a56436163fc4e510976b90f0d94","tid":2068034,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200617/photo/bkn-20200617170424736-0617_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200617170500\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A